WEBVTT

668bc758-5522-423d-8933-d1208dd419b4-0
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.252
The Internet offers a multitude
of ways to communicate and stay

668bc758-5522-423d-8933-d1208dd419b4-1
00:00:04.252 --> 00:00:05.320
in touch with others.

219d3c52-cf30-4f4c-9e45-e591b87bee0e-0
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:09.283
This includes services like
e-mail, instant messaging,

219d3c52-cf30-4f4c-9e45-e591b87bee0e-1
00:00:09.283 --> 00:00:13.191
website, discussion boards,
social media, and even voice and

219d3c52-cf30-4f4c-9e45-e591b87bee0e-2
00:00:13.191 --> 00:00:13.960
video calls.

65edb118-ffc6-40d6-8a5e-f978370af471-0
00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:17.432
On top of learning how to use
these various methods of

65edb118-ffc6-40d6-8a5e-f978370af471-1
00:00:17.432 --> 00:00:20.202
communication, it's also
important to understand when to

65edb118-ffc6-40d6-8a5e-f978370af471-2
00:00:20.202 --> 00:00:20.640
use them.

dbef95e5-5f52-4dae-8488-26444a457a1a-0
00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:24.969
For example, if you need to ask
a coworker a question that

dbef95e5-5f52-4dae-8488-26444a457a1a-1
00:00:24.969 --> 00:00:27.963
requires a time sensitive reply,
e-mail might not be the best

dbef95e5-5f52-4dae-8488-26444a457a1a-2
00:00:27.963 --> 00:00:30.522
choice as not everyone checks
their e-mail regularly

dbef95e5-5f52-4dae-8488-26444a457a1a-3
00:00:30.522 --> 00:00:31.440
throughout the day.

16fc0a92-c2a2-4b22-8a04-34b4e3d28013-0
00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:35.541
Instead, your company may use an
instant messaging service like

16fc0a92-c2a2-4b22-8a04-34b4e3d28013-1
00:00:35.541 --> 00:00:38.763
Kye or Google Hangouts or Lack,
and sending a textbased message

16fc0a92-c2a2-4b22-8a04-34b4e3d28013-2
00:00:38.763 --> 00:00:41.279
through that service may get you
a quicker reply.

288d4235-0216-4ef9-ad46-02f027c6793e-0
00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:45.072
In situations where you can wait
a reasonable amount of time for

288d4235-0216-4ef9-ad46-02f027c6793e-1
00:00:45.072 --> 00:00:47.880
a reply, e-mail is a better
choice as the general exectation

288d4235-0216-4ef9-ad46-02f027c6793e-2
00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.734
is that e-mail is not for back
and forth conversation in real

288d4235-0216-4ef9-ad46-02f027c6793e-3
00:00:50.734 --> 00:00:53.081
time, but instead let each
person be a little more

288d4235-0216-4ef9-ad46-02f027c6793e-4
00:00:53.081 --> 00:00:56.119
thoughtful about their words and
the information they're sharing.

7ef106ad-cd87-43b2-ac89-7a9bf7e0971f-0
00:00:56.870 --> 00:00:59.554
e-mail is also useful to have a
written record of your

7ef106ad-cd87-43b2-ac89-7a9bf7e0971f-1
00:00:59.554 --> 00:01:02.726
conversations and of course for
real time conversations when you

7ef106ad-cd87-43b2-ac89-7a9bf7e0971f-2
00:01:02.726 --> 00:01:05.752
can't be in the same room, you
have the option of traditional

7ef106ad-cd87-43b2-ac89-7a9bf7e0971f-3
00:01:05.752 --> 00:01:08.729
phone calls or even videobased
calls so you can both see and

7ef106ad-cd87-43b2-ac89-7a9bf7e0971f-4
00:01:08.729 --> 00:01:09.950
hear people in real time.

80bed246-bd68-4658-8c15-c645dcfb309b-0
00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:12.973
Video calls can make it a little
easier to communicate

80bed246-bd68-4658-8c15-c645dcfb309b-1
00:01:12.973 --> 00:01:15.573
effectively because they allow
you to see the expressions on

80bed246-bd68-4658-8c15-c645dcfb309b-2
00:01:15.573 --> 00:01:17.149
the attendees faces during the
call.

822910fe-ddca-40d7-8b88-70976f3fb546-0
00:01:18.070 --> 00:01:21.334
O Again, understanding when to
use certain types of services is

822910fe-ddca-40d7-8b88-70976f3fb546-1
00:01:21.334 --> 00:01:23.630
an important aspect of
communicating online.